Shadow Wing::

She looked around and felt anothoer shot hit the ship.
She transformed into owl mode. "I don't know about you love," she 
said to Lunarpine, "But I'm going outside.  I don't want to miss all 
the fun around here."
She flew up and down the hallway and towards the entrance of the ship.
